text: Björn Brönnum (born 16 September 1929) is a Danish rower. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics in Helsinki with the men's eight where they were eliminated in the semi-finals repêchage. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Danish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Frederiksberg Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
